Article.ArticleTitle: Complete genome sequence of a human enterovirus 71 strain isolated in wuhan, china, in 2010.

Abstract.AbstractText: The complete genome sequence of a human enterovirus 71 strain (EV71/wuhan/3018/2010), which was isolated in Wuhan in 2010, was amplified by a reverse transcription-PCR method and sequenced. Phylogenetic analysis based on the complete genome sequence classified this strain into subgenogroup A.
